  ~~~\r\n\r\n**Opcional:**\r\n\r\n  * Instalar o MySql Workbench executando o instalador (**mysql-workbench-community-6.3.6-winx64.msi**)\r\n\r\n  * Criar uma conexo chamada Local (root sem senha):\r\n![]( sem_senha.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n4.Criar Database do projeto (documentar depois)\r\n\r\n5.Procedimento padro de instalao Liferay\r\n\r\n  * Criar diretrio **Liferay** no *c:\\*\r\n  * Criar o subdiretrio **download**, dentro de *C:\\liferay*, e copiar os arquivos abaixo para dentro dele:\r\n\r\n   ~~~\r\nliferay-portal-tomcat-6.2-ce-ga6-20160112152609836.zip\r\nliferay-portal-doc-6.2-ce-ga6-20160112152609836.zip\r\nliferay-portal-src-6.2-ce-ga6-20160112152609836.zip\r\n   ~~~\r\n\r\n  * Extrair contedo do arquivo **liferay-ide-eclipse-windows-x64-2.2.4-ga5-201507230603.zip** no *c:\\Liferay*\r\n  * Executar o arquivo *c:\\Liferay\\eclipse\\eclipse.exe*, se apresentar erro, verificar o **passo 4.1** e testar novamente, **caso execute normalmente, ignorar** o passo 4.1 e fechar o eclipse.\r\n  * Criar o subdiretrio **bundles**, dentro do diretrio *c:\\Liferay*\r\n  * Extrair o contedo do arquivo **liferay-portal-tomcat-6.2-ce-ga6-20160112152609836.zip** no *c:\\Liferay\\bundles*\r\n  * Extrair o contedo do arquivo **liferay-plugins-sdk-6.2-ce-ga6-20160112152609836.zip** no *c:\\Liferay*\r\n  * Editar o arquivo *C:\\Liferay\\liferay-plugins-sdk-6.2\\build-common-ivy.xml*\r\n\r\n   Antes (Linha **120**):\r\n\r\n   ~~~\r\n	<if>\r\n		<not>\r\n			<available file=\"${ivy.home}/ivy-${ivy.version}.jar\" />\r\n		</not>\r\n		<then>\r\n			<mkdir dir=\"${ivy.home}\" />\r\n			\r\n			<mirrors-get\r\n				dest=\"${ivy.home}/ivy-${ivy.version}.jar\"\r\n				src=\"${ivy.jar.url}\"\r\n			/>\r\n		</then>\r\n	</if>\r\n   ~~~\r\n\r\n   Depois:\r\n\r\n   ~~~\r\n	<if>\r\n		<not>\r\n			<available file=\"${ivy.home}/ivy-${ivy.version}.jar\" />\r\n		</not>\r\n		<then>\r\n			<mkdir dir=\"${ivy.home}\" />\r\n        <setproxy proxyhost=\"192.168.10.1\" proxyport=\"3128\" proxyUser=\"\"    proxyPassword